! Per-tab tiddlers

Edit `$:/config/wikilabs/tw-mcp/per-tab-tiddlers` to extend or override which titles are treated as per-tab view state. The value is a TW filter; default:

```
[[$:/StoryList]] [[$:/HistoryList]] [prefix[$:/state/]]
```

Changes take effect on the next wiki change without restart.
